Natasha Elderfield is on trial for the murder of her boyfriend Robert Dobinson, 33, in Abingdon, Oxfordshire . 
  She is accused of stabbing him through the heart on the banks of the River Thames . 
  Mr Dobinson arrived home to find her in a short dress and stockings with her lover below deck . 
  Court heard she flew into a rage when he interrupted her attempts to have sex with another man . 
  Elderfield denies murder at Oxford Crown Court . 
 